<exercise checkit-seed="0005" checkit-slug="M4" checkit-title="Finding a matrix inverse">
  <statement>
      <p>Show how to find the inverse of the matrix <m>B=\left[\begin{array}{cccc}
-1 &amp; 0 &amp; -3 &amp; -1 \\
-1 &amp; 2 &amp; -4 &amp; -3 \\
0 &amp; -2 &amp; 5 &amp; -1 \\
2 &amp; -1 &amp; 5 &amp; 4
\end{array}\right]</m>.</p>
  </statement>
  <answer>
      <me>B^{-1}=\left[\begin{array}{cccc}
29 &amp; 22 &amp; 9 &amp; 26 \\
-13 &amp; -9 &amp; -4 &amp; -11 \\
-7 &amp; -5 &amp; -2 &amp; -6 \\
-9 &amp; -7 &amp; -3 &amp; -8
\end{array}\right]</me>
  </answer>
</exercise>
